Item.Name: Semi-milled or wholly milled rice
Item.Description: Semi-milled or wholly milled rice, whether or not polished or glazed

Item.Name: Natural rubber latex
Item.Description: Natural rubber latex, whether or not prevulcanised

Item.Name: Dextrins & other modified starches
Item.Description: Dextrins and other modified starches, e.g. pregelatinised or esterified starches

Item.Name: Pasta
Item.Description: Pasta, cooked or otherwise prepared (excluding stuffed)

Item.Name: Maize (excl seed for sowing)
Item.Description: Maize (excluding seed for sowing)

Item.Name: Smoked sheets of natural rubber
Item.Description: Smoked sheets of natural rubber

Item.Name: Compounded rubber, unvulcanised, in flat shapes
Item.Description: Compounded rubber, unvulcanised, in the form of plates, sheets or strip (excluding rubber compounded with carbon black or silica, and mixtures of natural rubber, balata, gutta-percha, guayule, chicle and similar natural gums containing synthetic rubber or factice derived from oils)

Item.Name: Bread, pastry
Item.Description: Bread, pastry, cakes, biscuits and other bakers' wares, whether or not containing cocoa; communion wafers, empty cachets of a kind suitable for pharmaceutical use, sealing wafers, rice paper and similar products (excluding crispbread, gingerbread and the like, sweet biscuits, waffles, wafers not mentioned, rusks, toasted bread and similar toasted products)

Item.Name: Vegetable fats, oil & fractions, hydrogenated, inter-esterified, etc.
Item.Description: Vegetable fats and oils and their fractions, partly or wholly hydrogenated, inter-esterified, re-esterified or elaidinised, whether or not refined, but not further prepared

Item.Name: Edible mixtures of fats, oil & fractions, chemically modified nes
Item.Description: Edible mixtures or preparations of animal or vegetable fats or oils and edible fractions of different fats or oils (excluding fats, oils and their fractions, partly or wholly hydrogenated, inter-esterified, re-esterified or elaidinised, whether or not refined, but not further prepared, mixtures of olive oils and their fractions, and solid margarine)

Item.Name: Uncooked pasta
Item.Description: Uncooked pasta, not stuffed or otherwise prepared, not containing eggs

Item.Name: Palm oil (excl crude) & fractions
Item.Description: Palm oil and its fractions, whether or not refined (excluding chemically modified and crude)

Item.Name: Mixtures of natural & synthetic rubber/factice, in primary forms
Item.Description: Mixtures of natural rubber, balata, gutta-percha, guayule, chicle or similar types of natural rubber with synthetic rubber or factice, in primary forms or in plates, sheets or strip

Item.Name: Tapioca
Item.Description: Tapioca and substitutes therefor prepared from starch, in the form of flakes, grains, pearls, siftings or similar forms

Item.Name: Cereals in worked grains, prepared, n.e.s.
Item.Description: Cereals (excluding maize [corn]) in grain or flake form or other worked grains, pre-cooked or otherwise prepared, n.e.s. (excluding flour, groats and meal, food preparations obtained by swelling or roasting or from unroasted cereal flakes or from mixtures of unroasted cereal flakes and roasted cereal flakes or swelled cereals and bulgur wheat)

Item.Name: Compounded rubber, unvulcanised, in primary forms
Item.Description: Compounded, unvulcanised rubber in primary forms (excluding solutions and dispersions, those containing carbon black or silica, mixtures of natural rubber, balata, gutta-percha, guayule, chicle or similar types of natural rubber with synthetic rubber or factice, and those in the form of plates, sheets or strip)

Item.Name: Fats, oil & fractions nes
Item.Description: Animal or vegetable fats and oils and their fractions, boiled, oxidised, dehydrated, sulphurised, blown, polymerised by heat in vacuum or in inert gas or otherwise chemically modified, inedible mixtures or preparations of animal or vegetable fats or oils or of fractions of different fats or oils, n.e.s.

Item.Name: Palm kernel & babassu oil (excl crude) & fractions
Item.Description: Palm kernel and babassu oil and their fractions, whether or not refined, but not chemically modified (excluding crude)

Item.Name: Synthetic rubber/factice derived from oils, in primary forms
Item.Description: Synthetic rubber and factice derived from oils, in primary forms or in plates, sheets or strip (excluding latex, styrene-butadiene rubber "SBR", carboxylated styrene-butadiene rubber "XSBR", butadiene rubber "BR", isobutylene isoprene rubber "IIR", halo-isobutene-isoprene rubber "CIIR" or "BIIR", chloroprene rubber "CR", acrylonitrile-butadiene rubber "NBR", isoprene rubber "IR" and non-conjugated ethylene-propylene diene rubber "EPDM")

Item.Name: Groats & meal of cereals nes
Item.Description: Groats and meal of cereals (excluding wheat and maize)
